OL,3,CGuernsey deputy blames Covid and
OL,4,CBrexit for decline in cruise passenger
OL,5,Cnumbers
OL,7,FA Guernsey deputy says a decline in
OL,8,Fcruise ship passengers is concerning
OL,9,Fbut is optimistic about the future of
OL,10,Fthe industry in the island.
OL,12,FDeputy Simon Vermeulen, who sits on
OL,13,FGuernsey's Committee for Economic
OL,14,FDevelopment and is the island's
OL,15,FTourism lead, told ITV News that there
OL,16,Fare concerted efforts to address the
OL,17,Fchallenge, saying: "Trust us. We're
OL,18,Fnot doing nothing.
