OL,3,CGuernsey deputy blames Covid and
OL,4,CBrexit for decline in cruise passenger
OL,5,Cnumbers
OL,7,F"We're working very hard, proactively.
OL,8,FWe're doing the arduous task and we're
OL,9,Fgetting results.
OL,11,F"You will see, in the next couple of
OL,12,Fyears, an increase (in passenger
OL,13,Fnumbers). You will see us back up to
OL,14,Fstrength again."
OL,16,FDeputy Vermeulen was speaking after
OL,17,FStates of Guernsey figures revealed
OL,18,Fcruise passenger numbers had dropped
OL,19,Fsignificantly this year.
