OL,3,CGuernsey deputy blames Covid and
OL,4,CBrexit for decline in cruise passenger
OL,5,Cnumbers
OL,7,F2024 has seen 37,651 cruise passengers
OL,8,Fland in Guernsey, far below 2023's
OL,9,F79,672 figure.
OL,11,FIn 2019, there were more than 100,000
OL,12,Fpassengers.
OL,14,FPoor weather has been attributed by
OL,15,Fsome for 2024's low passenger levels
OL,16,Fbut business owners and politicians
OL,17,Fare concerned about the wider decline
OL,18,Fin cruise ships visiting Guernsey.
