OL,5,Cnumbers
OL,7,FDeputy Vermeulen says Brexit and Covid
OL,8,Fhave added extra challenges in
OL,9,Fattracting cruise ships.
OL,11,FHe said: "What we have had is Covid
OL,12,Fand Brexit. Brexit hasn't helped. We
OL,13,Fused to be, traditionally, when we
OL,14,Fwere part of the EU, the last port, so
OL,15,Fthey (passengers) could stock up on
OL,16,Fduty free. Now that doesn't happen so
OL,17,Fmuch.
