OL,3,CGuernsey deputy blames Covid and
OL,4,CBrexit for decline in cruise passenger
OL,5,Cnumbers
OL,7,F"We are keen to get more of the
OL,8,Fbusiness back and there is a chance
OL,9,Fthat some of the people that aren't
OL,10,Fsailing to Guernsey this year might
OL,11,Fwell come back."
OL,13,FDeputy Vermeulen added that a working
OL,14,Fgroup he is part of a working group,
OL,15,Fset up in collaboration with Ports of
OL,16,FGuernsey and the island's
OL,17,FHarbourmaster, to try and attract more
OL,18,Fcruise ships to the island going
OL,19,Fforward.
