OL,3,CGuernsey deputy blames Covid and
OL,4,CBrexit for decline in cruise passenger
OL,5,Cnumbers
OL,7,F"We've got a little plan to improve
OL,8,Fthe harbour and where visitors are
OL,9,Fdropped off so that is part of our
OL,10,Fscheme. So that's been drawn up and
OL,11,Fthat's being shown to all the cruise
OL,12,Fliners to show how we're investing in
OL,13,Fthat for the future.
OL,15,F"That would enable us to have two or
OL,16,Fthree cruise liners on and off within
OL,17,Ftheir time limit."
OL,19,FDeputy Vermeulen described this work
OL,20,Fas "very positive".
