OL,5,Cnumbers
OL,7,FWhen asked about whether Guernsey has
OL,8,Flost its appeal for tourists, Deputy
OL,9,FVermeulen vehemently denied it was an
OL,10,Fissue.
OL,12,FHe said: "Guernsey's more attractive
OL,13,Fthan ever.
OL,15,F"There's no VAT in any of our shops.
OL,16,FWe've got a fantastic offering in our
OL,17,Fpubs. The culture, the Guernsey beer
OL,18,Fand the food that we offer. This is
OL,19,Fthe best seafood in the world that's
OL,20,Fon offer in Guernsey."
